## Mongoose

Constructor to
By default it connects to localhost mongoDB. If you want to connect to external db you need to provide a uri in the constructor

### Parameters

-   `mongoUri` **[string][5]** The mongoUri to connect
-   `options` **[object][6]** The options for connecting

### connectToMongoDb

This function connects to mongoDB.
By default it connects to localhost mongoDB. If you want to connect to external db you need to provide a uri in the constructor

#### Parameters

-   `callback` **[function][7]** The callback function

